Application: Agent Simple
  Description: Minimal AI agent — submit a prompt, get a completion
Id: 2b909f99-d936-4469-843c-2fdc6aceef60

Users authenticate with stub
Scopes are "agent.use"

An "anonymous" has "agent.use"

Content called "completions":
  Each completion has a prompt which is text, required
  Each completion has a response which is text
  Anyone with "agent.use" can view, create, or update completions

Compute called "complete":
  Provider is "llm"
  Accesses completions
  Input from field completion.prompt
  Output into field completion.response
  Trigger on event "completion.created"
  Directive is ```
    You are a helpful assistant. Be concise and clear.
    If you don't know the answer, say so honestly.
  ```
  Objective is ```
    Answer the following prompt from the user.
  ```
  Anyone with "agent.use" can execute this
  Audit level: actions
  Anyone with "agent.use" can audit

As an anonymous, I want to submit prompts and see responses
  so that I can test the AI agent:
    Show a page called "Agent"
    Display a table of completions with columns: prompt, response
    Accept input for prompt
    This table subscribes to completions changes

Navigation bar:
  "Agent" links to "Agent" visible to all

